# Ultra Clean Mobile Services

A modern mobile booking and management application built with Kivy and SQLite for Ultra Clean Mobile Services (PTY) Ltd.

## Overview

Ultra Clean Mobile Services allows customers to conveniently book cleaning services directly from their mobile device while providing business owners with a dashboard to manage bookings and service requests.

The application is designed for service-based businesses that offer on-site cleaning services.

## Features

### Customer Features
- Browse available cleaning services
- Book appointments directly through the app
- Select preferred date and time
- Provide service location and special instructions
- Receive booking confirmation

### Services Offered
- Mobile Car Washing
- Couch Cleaning
- Mattress Cleaning
- Rug Cleaning
- Curtain Cleaning
- Chair Cleaning
- Built-in Carpet Cleaning
- Specialized Upholstery Cleaning
- Ottoman Cleaning

### Business Owner Features
- Secure owner login
- View all bookings
- Filter bookings by status
- Booking statistics dashboard
- Update booking statuses:
  - Pending
  - Confirmed
  - Completed
  - Cancelled

### Database
- SQLite database integration
- Persistent booking storage
- Automatic database creation
- Booking history management

